---

## Sections Included

1. **Hero** – Animated TECH WIZARD 2.0 title, live countdown timer to 20 March 2026, event stats, Register Now / Learn More buttons
2. **About** – Event description with highlight cards + the official poster displayed
3. **Problem Categories** – 6 animated domain cards (Innovation, Women Safety, Smart Ag, MedTech, Disaster, Education)
4. **Schedule** – Day-by-day tabbed timeline (Day 0, Day 1, Day 2) with evaluation rounds highlighted
5. **Prizes** – Podium-style prize cards (₹2,500 / ₹2,000 / ₹1,500) + extras (certificates, goodies)
6. **Rules** – 9 numbered hackathon rules
7. **Gallery** – Image grid using all your photos (poster, logos, schedule, problems)
8. **Registration Form** → redirects to your Google Form
9. **Contact** – Shubham, Deepak, and official email
10. **Feedback Form** → redirects to your Google Form
11. **Footer** – Brand info, links, contact

