## ⚠️ Connect Your Google Forms

Open [script.js](file:///c:/Users/dyuti/OneDrive/Documents/TechWizard%202.0/script.js) and replace lines 7–8:

```js
const GOOGLE_FORM_REG_URL = 'https://forms.gle/YOUR_REGISTRATION_FORM_ID';
const GOOGLE_FORM_FB_URL  = 'https://forms.gle/YOUR_FEEDBACK_FORM_ID';
```

Paste in your actual Google Form short links (from **Forms → Send → link icon**).

---

## How to Open Locally

Double-click [index.html](file:///c:/Users/dyuti/OneDrive/Documents/TechWizard%202.0/index.html) — it opens directly in any browser. No server needed.
